HEADWORD: Tegula
<hw>Teg"u*la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Tegulae</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L., a tile, dim. fr.
<ets>tegere</ets> to cover.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small
